unsupported_device.description:
A Bluetooth device was detected that could not be identified as a supported adjustable bed.

**Device:** {name}
**Address:** `{address}`
**Reason:** {reason}

If this is an adjustable bed that you'd like to see supported, please [report it on GitHub]({github_url}) with as much information as possible about your bed model.

You can also run the **Run BLE Diagnostics** service with this device's address to capture protocol data that can help us add support.
